==Competitions==
===Overall===
As in nine out of the last ten seasons,<ref>[[FC Barcelona#Recent seasons|en.wikipedia.org: FC Barcelona on 30 May 2009]]</ref> Barcelona is going to be present in all major competitions: [[La Liga 2009-10|La Liga]], the [[UEFA Champions League 2009-10|UEFA Champions League]] and the [[Copa del Rey 2009-10|Copa del Rey]]. The previous season's treble success means that Barcelona will also contest the [[FIFA Club World Cup]], the [[European Super Cup]] and the [[Supercopa de EspaÃ±a]]. The side will also be present in the [[Copa Catalunya]].<br />
